<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>FAQs</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <!-- Icon -->
        <link href="@Url.Content("~/image/book-shop.png")" rel="icon" type="image/x-icon">

    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <style type="text/css">
      body{
        background: #eee;
        padding-top: 20px;
        font-family: monospace;
      }
      .faq-header{
        border-radius: 20px 20px 0px 0px;
        padding: 10px 0px;
        background: #27ae60;
        color: #fff;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-content: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .faq-item{
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }
      .faq-body{
        display: none;
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: justify;
      }
      .faq-wrapper{
        width: 75%;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .faq-inner{
        padding: 30px;
        background: aliceblue;
      }
      .faq-plus{
        float: right;
        font-size: 1.4em;
        line-height: 1em;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      hr{
        background-color: #9b9b9b;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="faq-wrapper">
          <div class="faq-header">
            <h1>FAQs</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-inner">
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>
                About Us?
                <span class="faq-plus">&plus;</span>
              </h3>
              <div class="faq-body">
                FPT Book Store is a leading book retailer in Vietnam, with a reputation for providing a wide range of high-quality books
                and exceptional customer service. The store offers a diverse selection of books, including bestsellers, educational
                texts, academic journals, and children's books. FPT Book Store has become a popular destination for book lovers in
                Vietnam, who appreciate the store's commitment to quality and its efforts to promote reading and knowledge in the
                community. With a strong online presence and an extensive network of physical stores across the country, FPT Book Store
                is dedicated to making books accessible to everyone, and has become a trusted source for readers of all ages and
                interests.
              </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>
                How can I purchase books from FPT Book Store? 
                <span class="faq-plus">&plus;</span>
              </h3>
              <div class="faq-body">
                You can purchase books from FPT Book Store through their physical stores or their online store. For online purchases,
                simply visit their website, select the books you want, and follow the checkout process. Please note that we don't have
                online payment yet, so you will need to pay for your purchase at our physical store or via bank transfer.
              </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>
                I dont see my name in the profile page?
                <span class="faq-plus">&plus;</span>
              </h3>
              <div class="faq-body">
                When you log in to the website for the first time, you will need to update your profile with your personal and contact details first. This is required to complete your purchase and for us to deliver your books to you.
              </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>
                Do I need to create an account to purchase books on FPT Book Store's website?
                <span class="faq-plus">&plus;</span>
              </h3>
              <div class="faq-body">
                You need to create an account on our website to purchase books. This allows us to process your orders and track
                your purchases. Additionally, creating an account also gives you access to our loyalty program and other exclusive
                promotions. </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>
                Do you have a lockout feature to prevent unauthorized access to accounts on FPT Book Store's website?
                <span class="faq-plus">&plus;</span>
              </h3>
              <div class="faq-body">
                We have a lockout feature that activates after a certain number of unsuccessful login attempts. This helps prevent
                unauthorized access to your account and ensures the security of your personal information. If you find that your account
                has been locked out, please contact our customer service team for assistance.</div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>
                Does FPT Book Store ban accounts that violate the website's terms of service?
                <span class="faq-plus">&plus;</span>
              </h3>
              <div class="faq-body">
                We reserve the right to ban accounts that violate our website's terms of service, such as engaging in fraudulent or
                abusive behavior. We take the security and privacy of our customers seriously and will take appropriate action to
                protect our users and our platform.</div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>
                Do you have two-factor authentication (2FA) to protect accounts on FPT Book Store's website?
                <span class="faq-plus">&plus;</span>
              </h3>
              <div class="faq-body">
                We offer two-factor authentication (2FA) as an additional layer of security to protect your account. We highly
                recommend enabling 2FA to help prevent unauthorized access to your account and keep your personal information safe.
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
@RenderBody()
    <script type="text/javascript">
      $(".faq-plus").on('click',function(){
        $(this).parent().parent().find('.faq-body').slideToggle();
      });
    </script>
  </body>

</html>